8680 /******************************************************************************/

8682 /* Ethernet MAC Registers bits definitions */
8683 /* */
8684 /******************************************************************************/
8685 /* Bit definition for Ethernet MAC Control Register register */
8686 #define ETH_MACCR_WD ((uint32_t)0x00800000U) /* Watchdog disable */
8687 #define ETH_MACCR_JD ((uint32_t)0x00400000U) /* Jabber disable */
8688 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG ((uint32_t)0x000E0000U) /* Inter-frame gap */
8689 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_96Bit ((uint32_t)0x00000000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 96Bit */
8690  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_88Bit ((uint32_t)0x00020000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 88Bit */
8691  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_80Bit ((uint32_t)0x00040000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 80Bit */
8692  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_72Bit ((uint32_t)0x00060000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 72Bit */
8693  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_64Bit ((uint32_t)0x00080000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 64Bit */
8694  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_56Bit ((uint32_t)0x000A0000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 56Bit */
8695  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_48Bit ((uint32_t)0x000C0000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 48Bit */
8696  #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_40Bit ((uint32_t)0x000E0000U) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 40Bit */
8697 #define ETH_MACCR_CSD ((uint32_t)0x00010000U) /* Carrier sense disable (during transmission) */
8698 #define ETH_MACCR_FES ((uint32_t)0x00004000U) /* Fast ethernet speed */
8699 #define ETH_MACCR_ROD ((uint32_t)0x00002000U) /* Receive own disable */
8700 #define ETH_MACCR_LM ((uint32_t)0x00001000U) /* loopback mode */
8701 #define ETH_MACCR_DM ((uint32_t)0x00000800U) /* Duplex mode */
8702 #define ETH_MACCR_IPCO ((uint32_t)0x00000400U) /* IP Checksum offload */
8703 #define ETH_MACCR_RD ((uint32_t)0x00000200U) /* Retry disable */
8704 #define ETH_MACCR_APCS ((uint32_t)0x00000080U) /* Automatic Pad/CRC stripping */
